# This file is intentionally empty.
#
# Repository-wide pnpm configuration is consolidated in pnpm-workspace.yaml (the
# preferred location starting in pnpm 10). This file is kept so that:
#   - settings that can only be expressed in .npmrc (e.g. registry auth tokens
#     written by CI tooling) have a project-level target file, and
#   - any future per-project options that don't have a pnpm-workspace.yaml
#     equivalent have an obvious place to land.
